{"tid":2377190,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"賤男YouTuber連環嗒偶像艷星 揭毒打F Cup京佳","createTime":"2021-01-23T11:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T12:48:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":45,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f660fc4e06d56085b149eb06320a1fdeef23b436","tid":2377190,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:30:05.000Z","msg":"日本女星今泉佑唯前日承認未婚懷孕，經手人是以YouTuber身份活躍網絡的MAHOTO，可是奉子成婚消息曝光後，驚爆MAHOTO迫一名15歲女學生拍裸照，更要求對方把學生証與性器官一同拍入鏡頭。醜聞曝光後，MAHOTO所屬的UUUM事務所已將他炒魷，事件還驚動日本警方。<br />\n<br />\n22歲的今泉佑唯正懷孕五個月，她是去年透過朋友認識MAHOTO，拍拖未夠一年已搞出人命。其實，28歲的MAHOTO早有前科，他前年爆出施暴當時的同居女性偶像，被捕後遭公司雪藏，雙方達成和解，但MAHOTO仍死性不改。有日媒爆料，該位被打女星，就是曾經來港跟陳柏宇代言飲品的F Cup偶像京佳，消息指她前年遭MAHOTO虐打，京佳的頭慘被男方踩踏，最終報警求助，治療兩星期才告康復，更要一度停工休養。<br />\n<br />\nMAHOTO更是圈中食家，被爆至少與七位圈中女性扯上關係，亦搭上現年24歲的巨乳女星都丸紗也華，MAHOTO又跟AKB48的21歲現役成員市川愛美於六年前流出合照，不過他事後在Twitter否認緋聞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_2_uun9VljqsGzmheOOdWACAqQQ=/802x1200/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KNKW3FM665FV3BQEB4ZOAY5S4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_2_uun9VljqsGzmheOOdWACAqQQ%3D%2F802x1200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKNKW3FM665FV3BQEB4ZOAY5S4E.jpg&h=8327450f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7aUZtjY40hCOY0zgG2qxkPdUtk0=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BCDQLCFAE5FBXCBV2VVSE67N5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7aUZtjY40hCOY0zgG2qxkPdUtk0%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBCDQLCFAE5FBXCBV2VVSE67N5Q.jpg&h=cbfaf4aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e62fd8f839e1aa3b29045327f130ea19b86e205","tid":2377190,"uid":229026,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:30:50.000Z","